    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName> riceve da
                            <persName key="#Subdeacons"><name ref="Danihel">Daniel</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Subdeacons">subdiaconus</rs> filio <persName>bone memorie <name
                                ref="Andreas">Andree</name></persName> (…) livellario nomine (…) <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casa et res</rs> illa in loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/3339"
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >Villa Orbana</placeName>, qui modo regitur per <persName><name
                                ref="Ildus">Ildo</name></persName> et pertenens <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/132"
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Emperor/king #Churches #Subdeacons #vassusOf"
                            >Sancti Silvester</orgName>, quas tu per <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                ><rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libello</rs> abis da
                                <persName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals #Emperor/king #vassusOf"
                                ref="#people/3313">Ghisalmari</persName>
                            <rs key="#Emperor/king #vassusOf">vuasso domni imperatoris</rs></rs>;
                        suprascripta casa cum terris, vineis, olivis, silvis, virgareis, pratis,
                        pascuis, (…); la manterrà dum tu per libello abis. Obbligo: homines in ipsa
                        casa ad residendum et abitandum mittere debeamus, et tam ipsa casa et res
                        bene laborare et gubernare seo in omnibus meliorare (…) Censo: per singulos
                        annos, usque dum eas per ipso libello abis, rendere debeamus medietatem
                        vinum puro a tertiam vices uba legitime calcata et indi vinata, nam non
                        pondum levandum et medietate oleo; et per homnem mense aprelis (…) argentum
                        denarios bonos expendivilis numero sesaginta septe; et per homne Cena Domini
                        (…) pario pulli cum ovas decem; et a mandato tuo hic Luca venire debeamus
                        iustitiam faciendum; et si tu aut misso tuo ibidem per vindemmia super
                        palmentum veneritis, nos vos recipere et gubernare debeamus tantum (…).
                        Pena: argentum solidos viginti (…). <persName key="#Writer #Witness #Notary"
                                ><name ref="Lopo">Lopo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Churches">Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudemundus">Teudimundus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudebertus"
                            >Teupertus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Notary #Scabini"
                                ><name ref="Adalfredus">Adalfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Gundalbrandus"
                            >Gundelprandus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Adremundus">Atrimundo</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>ChLA, 83, n. 38, pp. 126-127; MDL, 5/2, n. 854, p. 522</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
                <p>Sul vassallo imperiale Ghiselmario, vd. Schneider 1975: 300; Castagnetti 2010:
                    255-256. Sulla serie di livelli accordati dal diacono Daniele e sulle vicende
                    della chiesa di S. Silvestro di Lucca, vd. Stoffella 2014: 49-66; Tomei 2014:
                    542-546; Viti 2019-2020: 129-131.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="links">
                <p/>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sottoscrizioni autografe: Teudimundus, Teupertus, Adalfridi, Gundelprandus,
                    Atrimundo, Lopo notarius (scrittore). Sottoscrizioni con
                        <foreign>Signa</foreign>: Iohannes (autore). Note tergali: di mano del
                    rogatario: <foreign>libello ad I[o]h[anne …15…]</foreign>; di mano dell’XI:
                        <foreign>l(ivellum) d(e) casa et re in Villa Urbana</foreign>.</p>
            </div>
